to learn about encryption.</span></li><li value=3D"2"><span>Can be physical=
ly implemented, such as with a set of rotating disks or a set of cards, kno=
wn as a scytale, which can be useful in certain situations.</span></li><li =
value=3D"3"><span>Requires only a small set of pre-shared information.</spa=
n></li><li value=3D"4"><span>Can be modified easily to create a more secure=
