</ul><h3 id=3D"disadvantages" style=3D"text-align:left"><span>Disadvantages=
</span></h3><ul><li value=3D"1"><span>It is not secure against modern decry=
ption methods.</span></li><li value=3D"2"><span>Vulnerable to known-plainte=
xt attacks, where an attacker has access to both the encrypted and unencryp=
