n></a><span> as it would be easy to crack.</span></li><li value=3D"5"><span=
>It is not suitable for secure communication as it is easily broken.</span>=
</li><li value=3D"6"><span>Does not provide confidentiality, integrity, and=
 authenticity in a message.&nbsp;</span></li></ul><h3 id=3D"features-of-cae=
sar-cipher" style=3D"text-align:left"><b><strong>Features of Caesar Cipher<=
/strong></b></h3><ol><li value=3D"1"><b><strong>Substitution cipher:</stron=
